Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把这些箱子全部打开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要全部打开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生太短暂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人一生中能打开的数量是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手肿了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况持续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手会僵硬掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回医院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手 手会废掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能画画的话我也会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老师打的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我以三倍还给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 这里正好是医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经决定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着 能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算什么都没留下来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想画画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生除此之外没有别的选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚对我说的那些话真的让我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会一直看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你哥哥的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住他好好地告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把昨晚告诉我的那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大声地告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老师找到的话一定会杀了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被打过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我以四倍偿还了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止四倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想狠狠揍他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说不想让她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能让她自己做主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次来真的了 那位大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾她是你的责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋不顾身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没办法赢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久 手怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把阿修的人生交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道能不能还给你就说了这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直画画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和我在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用还给我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地间的轮廓变得模模糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛能把我也吸进去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然是阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修司已经从东京回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去房间看他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢阿修的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有书本的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有放着速写本和画具的柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢雨的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种让人静下来的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛在温柔地抚摸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山 树 草 屋檐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久 修司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜切好了 要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 相处得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修就像雨一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修就像雨一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到他我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的时候他一定会来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是温柔地把手伸给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是简单地说放弃就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是放弃就能让自己解脱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要觉得自己是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在你身边陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 阿修肯定是我的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他在一起的时候就能深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己像树和草一样不停地成长起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是用一张困惑的脸温柔地笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我抱一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这是朝阳还是晚霞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 钟上显示的是五点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候的五点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点什么吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耀 耀眼……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这个更耀眼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮得让人睁不开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮得像涂上了一层油膜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是早上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种光辉的一定是早上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店也只有便利店开着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱打喷嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把病毒传到我身上了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个连棉被都没有的地方睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体会变差也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该稍微表示下关心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个易拉胡椒大蒜香肠是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以随便拿来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久没选这种男人真是英明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说阿久选择了老师实在太正确了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好象你都相通了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甘心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想多她该选我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是想来想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得能让她幸福的不是我也不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我为什么要被你教训
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙明明早就被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 被甩了 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我觉得你被甩了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不让阿久选择你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个乳臭未干的小毛孩 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子 穷瘪三 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有才能也没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿久选择了老师真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正会被甩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其靠钱和才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若对方是付出更多的温柔和诚实 这会让我轻松很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能 说到才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样人们随意地喜欢着 怨着 恨着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后什么都不说就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是枉然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想放弃所有的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想向柔弱的她撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那位大叔才能带给她幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早之前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（瞎搅和　竹本的脚　森田的脚 打架 要打架吗）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（青空 年轻人 河堤 风）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（青春）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天的拳击练习太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要参加高中校际比赛了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以热情比较高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制不了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们回学校去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 我回想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架也很美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是年轻时代的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚坐着就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩和腰都疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这箱子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一定要帮我把她的病治好）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实帮了个大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会如数还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过钱会还给你 阿久不会还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会把她治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让她重新拿起画笔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 喜欢 很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 终于表白了  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春 青春 青春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花本老师喜欢阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁给我拿瓶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿瓶酒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在一直看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 蜂蜜与三叶草
